  "actionable_ascii_heavy_residuals": [],
  "accepted_ascii_heavy_residuals": [
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:0",
      "text": "RenderMan for Maya 支持多种 render scene 的方式。",
      "ascii_letters": 27,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:1",
      "text": "Preview Rendering",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:2",
      "text": "Interactive Rendering in Maya",
      "ascii_letters": 26,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:3",
      "text": "Batch Rendering",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:4",
      "text": "render 完成的 scene 包含许多部分。从处理 quality 到为后续 compositing 选择合适 outputs，本 section 覆盖所有这些 topics。",
      "ascii_letters": 49,
      "cjk_chars": 27
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:6",
      "text": "为了理解 noise removal 和 anti-aliasing 的工作方式，我们为用户说明",
      "ascii_letters": 24,
      "cjk_chars": 17
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:7",
      "text": "Sampling",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:9",
      "text": "Filtering",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:11",
      "text": "Trace Depth",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:12",
      "text": "控制 trace depth 可以改变 scene 的 look 和 performance。不同 integrators 对这些 settings 的处理也不同。RenderMan 让这些 parameters 的 tuning 更容易，从而在 resource constraints 内达到所需 look。",
      "ascii_letters": 97,
      "cjk_chars": 34
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:13",
      "text": "Interactive Rendering and Checkpointing",
      "ascii_letters": 36,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:14",
      "text": "Progressive/",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:15",
      "text": "Interactive",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:16",
      "text": "Rendering 可以轻松 tuning scene materials 和 lights。",
      "ascii_letters": 35,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:17",
      "text": "Checkpointing",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:18",
      "text": "and Recovery 会把这种 progressive feature 扩展到 final renders，让你可以在 renders refine 过程中创建 save points。你可以用它更快 approval incomplete frames，并从停止处继续，而不浪费宝贵的 CPU cycles。",
      "ascii_letters": 97,
      "cjk_chars": 38
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:19",
      "text": "Diagnostics",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:20",
      "text": "RenderMan",
      "ascii_letters": 9,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:21",
      "text": "diagnostics",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:22",
      "text": "可帮助你在易读 display 中可视化 scene performance。有时可能不清楚 scene 最耗费 time 或 resources 的位置，但我们的 diagnostic output 会帮助你定位即使最隐蔽的 performance information。",
      "ascii_letters": 79,
      "cjk_chars": 41
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:23",
      "text": "Holdouts and Outputs",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:25",
      "text": "workflow 对于将 CG objects 集成到 live action plates 中至关重要。在某些 applications 中，这可能像点击一个 button 一样简单。为了改善 compositing integration，甚至改善 fully rendered shots，RenderMan 使用强大的",
      "ascii_letters": 100,
      "cjk_chars": 40
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:27",
      "text": "，让 compositing 中的 adjustments 更容易且更强大，并提供 ultimate flexibility。",
      "ascii_letters": 41,
      "cjk_chars": 13
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:29",
      "text": "在 rendering 中复用某些 data 可以简化 asset management，并提高 rendering efficiency。",
      "ascii_letters": 47,
      "cjk_chars": 13
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:31",
      "text": "提供 bake 到 2D 或 point cloud output 的方法。",
      "ascii_letters": 21,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:32",
      "text": "Nested Dielectrics",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:33",
      "text": "在 rendering 会彼此交互的 surfaces 时，尤其是 transparent/refractive surfaces，理解",
      "ascii_letters": 46,
      "cjk_chars": 13
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:34",
      "text": "Intersect Priority",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "ce958b0c16:35",
      "text": "settings 很重要。Intersect priority 允许用户简单地添加 attributes，即可获得正确 refractions，而无需通过繁琐 modeling 来解决问题。",
      "ascii_letters": 54,
      "cjk_chars": 30
    }
  ],
